{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"43662-topivala","title":"टोपीवाला","description":"‘टोपीवाला’ टोपी बेच्दै हिड्‌ने एकजना व्यापारीको कथा हो । यो कथा सुन्ने र सुनाउने परम्परामा आधारित छ । थाकेको व्यापारी रूखको छहारीमा निदाउदा बादरले सबै टोपी लगिदिन्छन्‌ । टोपी फर्काउन व्यापारीले गरेको चलाखी खुब रमाइलो छ । सिङ्‌गो कथा पढी आनन्द लिउँ । राम्रो लागे अरुलाई पनि सुनाउँ ।","language":"Nepali","langCode":"ne","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Ananta Prasad  Wagle"],"illustrators":["Promina Shreshtha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/43662-topivala"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99662/size3/4e79c2e7aeb406dc9588bd74870882f3.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99662/size6/4e79c2e7aeb406dc9588bd74870882f3.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81555/size6/5fe29834e5af956e6223cd41350cdb6b.jpg","text":"टोपीवाला टोपी बेच्दै गाउँ डुलिरहेको थियो ।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81556/size6/3049a459d7d539bca7a763a81ac57fd5.jpg","text":"हिँड्दा–हिँड्दा उसलाई थकाइ लाग्यो ।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81557/size6/ca40e0217b1a0a47d30be458aa100b4a.jpg","text":"ऊ एउटा रूखमुनि थकाइ मार्न बस्यो ।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81558/size6/cc519792b80fa4aeeabfeb93987f3a55.jpg","text":"धेरै थाकेकाले टोपीवाला रूखको फेदमै निदायो ।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81559/size6/6a042abdcc3b6ff9600bbb45a114a23e.jpg","text":"त्यस रूखमा बसेका बाँदरहरूले निदाइ रहेको टोपीवालालाई देखे ।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81560/size6/68790012dfb82171c7e473c35900ae42.jpg","text":"बाँदरहरू सुरुक्क रूखमुनि आए ।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81561/size6/aa05a8eeb14cf20a65091c25c22cf44d.jpg","text":"तिनले टोपीवालाको झोला खोतले । \nझोलामा रङ्गीचङ्गी टोपीहरू देखेर बाँदरहरू दङ्ग परे ।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81562/size6/3f33f8a40781971bffcc570a28cd98f2.jpg","text":"बाँदरहरूले एक–एक वटा रङ्गीचङ्गी टोपी लगाए ।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81563/size6/56596bc204018b6af41b5e5c37baf66a.jpg","text":"रातो, नीलो, हरियो, पहेँलो, सुन्तला, वैजनी र गुलाफी रङका टोपी लगाएका बाँदरहरू खुसीले नाच्न थाले ।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81564/size6/cde67bc56963bfe89c763e186a1ea1ee.jpg","text":"निदाइरहेको टोपीवाला चल्मलायो । बाँदरहरू फेरि रूखको हाँगा–हाँगामा पुगे । \nकेहीबेरपछि टोपीवाला ब्युँझियो ।","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81565/size6/110f3ade8f6dbc04952f966c1b99a66a.jpg","text":"बाँदरहरू छक्क पर्दै टोपीवालालाई हेर्न थाले ।","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81566/size6/a4278983fd4878bffebebfba5be2735b.jpg","text":"टोपीवालाले हतपत झोला हेऱ्यो । झोला रित्तै देखेर उसलाई साह्रै पीर पऱ्यो ।","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81567/size6/d7c5244fc08b609e813321c09349c812.jpg","text":"टोपीवालाले यसो माथि हेऱ्यो । रूखमा आफ्ना टोपी लगाएका बाँदरहरू देखेर पहिले त ऊ छक्क पऱ्यो। \nत्यसपछि उसलाई रिस पनि उठ्यो ।","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81568/size6/659e509e1580d5825a748500555f3936.jpg","text":"टोपीवालाले कसरी आफ्ना टोपीहरू फर्काउने भनी विचार गऱ्यो ।","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81569/size6/a7d2f7a8126daa8ed3a5f1d9509e50c2.jpg","text":"उसले आफ्नो टाउकोमा लगाइ रहेको टोपी फुकालेर रूखमाथि रहेका बाँदरहरूतिर मिल्कायो ।","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81570/size6/a166f1974723803c725589761368a106.jpg","text":"आफूलाई हिर्काएको सम्झेर बाँदरहरू पनि रिसाए ।","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81571/size6/edc16f67c2af2811a1ce2e4fcfe6cc87.jpg","text":"अनि उनीहरूले पनि \nआ–आफ्नो टाउकोबाट टोपी झिकेर टोपीवालातिर मिल्काए।","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81572/size6/963cf1ecbb2bb1c6f54a21764d6bc491.jpg","text":"आफ्ना सबै टोपी बटुलेर टोपीवालाले झोलामा हाल्यो । अनि टोपीवाला हाँस्दै–हाँस्दै बाटो लाग्यो । बाँदरहरूले छक्क पर्दै टोपीवालालाई हेरिरहे ।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":18,"words":189}}